{"tid":1532231,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"致香港人的原創歌曲 <自遊 | Be Water> - Teargas慎入","createTime":"2019-09-02T12:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T01:27:51.000Z","uid":234807,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6e703c4193eb92dda85a29ce9bb7d70a47ccf8ea","tid":1532231,"uid":234807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:57:46.000Z","msg":"幫fd重post<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">就算失望，不能絕望</span></span><br />\n<br />\n從6月 到831, 多少個無眠夜<br />\n希望小小歌曲可以慰藉同路人的心靈<br />\n堅守信念 相信香港會得到真正的自由<br />\n說好了 在那天煲底口罩脫下來相擁<br />\n<br />\n代作者嘅朋友嘅朋友嘅朋友post<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W7AZdzXXJQc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DW7AZdzXXJQc&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1ahjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=bfcbb159\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W7AZdzXXJQc</a>"},{"pid":"fdf14b6e70c9585048cd0ff4eeef43f5c4d3dc07","tid":1532231,"uid":234807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:58:38.000Z","msg":"作者的話:<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，<br />\n我已經冇創作音樂多年，但每次睇LIVE隔住個MON都感受到香港人不屈不撓嘅精神同無比嘅勇氣，<br />\n加埋啲創意無限，遍地開花嘅高質文宣圖，<br />\n深深打動左我去寫呢首歌<br />\n想同大家講<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">「路漫漫其修遠兮，吾將上下而求索」</span>，大家迷茫時記住勿忘初衷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">「兄弟爬山 各自努力」</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「齊上齊落 永不割蓆」</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">「光復香港 時代革命」</span>"},{"pid":"0745b38363549639bab0f1b70cd9c9963ba3615a","tid":1532231,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:59:25.000Z","msg":"十點鳩叫行動！！！！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Av5cBad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAv5cBad.jpg&h=53535c10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p4pT43z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp4pT43z.jpg&h=df08fc7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TH9T43A.j