係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"986415fa6bd9b1d3eada187d25b3276a43d0a1f3","tid":1532231,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573632b9f078dbd8e17bb22ab47f4e1dd04582c3","tid":1532231,"uid":196771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879422d249b13705f2843e412be5eb74a3fcc841","tid":1532231,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6175ffb3e404a748d0f7d0623a5e55c25fa756d","tid":1532231,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873a143c1e40e97b75c6dda87380f687bf50e4cc","tid":1532231,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/